New Update Features:
1. Added 4 new themes in addition to the original white one: **White + Red** and **Red + Blue**.
2. Added the ability for coaches to **train with a trainee On Floor** in the Online Coach section.
3. Added **in-app pop-up notifications** feature.
4. If a user subscribes to **Online Training**, they get **3 months of free access** to the Custom Exercises section.
5. Added the option to **attach instructional videos** while creating exercises for clients in the Online Training section.
6. Added the option to **attach illustrative images** while creating exercises in the Custom Exercises section.
7. Added the ability to **edit ready-made workouts freely**.
8. Introduced a **Referral Code** feature — when a user shares the app with another user, both receive **20% off any serial number** and **20 reward points**, where each point equals **1% discount**.
9. Fixed several bugs and **improved app performance**.
10. Added new **security measures** to make the app more stable and secure.

يشمل التحديث الجديد للتطبيق إضافة 4 ثيمات جديدة إلى الثيمات الأساسية، متابعة مدربين "On floor" في قسم التدريب أونلاين، إشعارات منبثقة، و3 أشهر مجانية للتمارين المخصصة للمشتركين في التدريب أونلاين. كما يدعم إضافة فيديوهات وصور توضيحية أثناء إنشاء التمارين، تعديل التمارين الجاهزة، نظام كود دعوة يمنح خصم 20% و20 نقطة (كل نقطة خصم 1%)، بالإضافة إلى حل المشاكل، تحسين الأداء، وتعزيز الأمان لأكبر استقرار.
-------------------
The new app update includes adding 4 new themes to the existing ones (white, white + red, red + blue), following "On floor" trainers in the online coaching section, pop-up notifications, and 3 free months of custom workouts for online training subscribers. It also supports adding explanatory videos and images during workout creation, editing ready-made workouts, an invitation code system offering 20% discount and 20 points (each point as 1% discount), plus fixing issues, improving performance, and enhancing security for greater stability.
